col IR format a2
SELECT SQL_ID, CHILD_NUMBER, PLAN_HASH_VALUE, IS_REOPTIMIZABLE IR
FROM V$SQL WHERE SQL_ID='&v_sql_id' ORDER BY SQL_ID, CHILD_NUMBER;

Directives are created only when dynamic sampling is set to 11, at session or system level.
show parameter OPTIMIZER_DYNAMIC_SAMPLING
SELECT TO_CHAR(D.DIRECTIVE_ID) DIR_ID, D.REASON FROM DBA_SQL_PLAN_DIRECTIVES D, DBA_SQL_PLAN_DIR_OBJECTS O
WHERE D.DIRECTIVE_ID=O.DIRECTIVE_ID AND O.OWNER = 'SOE' AND O.OBJECT_NAME='CUSTOMERS2' ORDER BY 1;

